{"type": "article", "id": 30173, "title": "像火烈鸟的茶具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-26T23:02:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160726225618iGgdeb1tCMYFKJco.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.roxanneflick.com/purpur_en.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purpur</a> 是德国普福尔茨海姆大学（Pforzheim University）毕业生 <a href=\"http://www.roxanneflick.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Roxanne Flick</a> 的作品，她将火烈鸟从水中捕鱼的过程与人们滤茶的方式联系在了一起。茶壶和糖罐的出水口被设计成像是火烈鸟脖子一样弯曲的形状，与它们圆鼓鼓的“身材”结合在一起，看上去生动活泼。Purpur 采用粉浆浇注法烧制而成，随后分别注入淡灰色和粉色的颜料。Flick 还为茶杯设计了配套的橡木制杯座，用这样一组就好像是小火烈鸟一样的茶具泡茶喝，仿佛空气中充溢的茶香也更加清甜了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726225637dxfLiVpC3oKFsaAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726225637yzWQd3eDSwl2aO91.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.048077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726225637Xm139PsVqS7QMBwW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607262256371T3R6EyBY9XqavmK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}